Black Friday has not officially launched yet, but many stores are holding great sales in the weeks leading up to the shopping day. These “pre-Black Friday deals” may just be discounted enough to tempt you into a purchase, if you are not a fan of long queues at physical stores or slow load times on websites. The price you are willing to pay now is known as the “I don’t feel like shopping in a frenzy on Black Friday so I will just buy it now and pay a bit more” quotient. Here are this week’s tech deals.                 